  "title": "Sales Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Greeting customers and offering assistance upon entry.<br>\nIdentifying customer needs and providing relevant product recommendations.<br>\nAnswering customer questions about products, promotions, and store policies.<br>\nHandling customer complaints and resolving issues.<br>\nProviding excellent customer service to ensure satisfaction.</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales and Transactions:</strong>Processing sales transactions accurately, including cash, card, and online payments.<br>\nHandling returns and refunds according to company policy.<br>\nOperating point-of-sale (POS) systems.<br>\nMeeting or exceeding sales targets.</li>\n  <li><strong>Inventory and Store Maintenance:</strong>Restocking shelves and maintaining a fully stocked store.<br>\nCreating and maintaining appealing product displays.<br>\nEnsuring the sales floor is clean, organized, and presentable.<br>\nAssisting with inventory management and receiving new shipments.</li>\n  <li><strong>Product Knowledge:</strong>Staying up-to-date on product information and features.<br>\nExplaining product benefits to customers.<br>\nProviding product demonstrations.</li>\n  <li><strong>General Support:</strong>Following all company policies and procedures.<br>\nCollaborating with other team members to ensure smooth store operations.<br>\nReporting any inventory or service issues to management.Gathering customer feedback to improve the shopping experience.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>",
