    "description": "<p>A well-established school, Symphony Music School has a long history in music education. We provide a favorable environment for learning music, conduct examinations (ABRSM, LCM and Rockschool) and hold concerts for our students, from children to adults. Popular courses include the Classical Piano, Violin, and Guitar. To harmonize the enthusiasm and passion for music presented by our prestigious customers and students, we explore and seek round the globe to provide you with the widest range of affordable musical instruments and accessories. </p>\n",
